Certainly! Here are some example sentences using the Serbian word "ceni" in different forms and positions:

1. On *ceni* svoje zdravlje. (He values his health.) 
2. Cenim tvoju iskrenost. (*I value* your honesty.) 
3. Vi *cenite* svoje zaposlene. (You value your employees.) 
4. Oni *cene* ovaj proizvod. (They value this product.) 
5. Kupac je *cenio* kvalitet usluge. (The customer valued the quality of service.) 
6. *Cenila* sam njegovu podršku. (I valued his support.) 
7. Ne možeš *ceniti* nešto što ne razumeš. (You can't value something you don't understand.) 
8. *Cenim sebe* i svoj rad. (I value myself and my work.) 

I hope this helps!